{"word":"Joram","slug":"joram","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Joram</b> <a href=\"#/H3141\">H3141</a> <br/> 1. A son of Toi<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=10'>2Sa 8:10</a> <br/> - Called Hadoram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=10'>1Ch 18:10</a> <br/> 2. Called Jehoram:<br/> - King of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=17'>2Ki 1:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=1'>2Ki 3:1</a> <br/> - King of Syria sends Naaman to, that he may be healed of his leprosy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=27'>2Ki 5:27</a> <br/> - Has war with the king of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=23'>2Ki 6:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=7'>2Ki 7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=29'>2Ki 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=6'>2Ch 22:6</a> <br/> - Inquires for the particulars concerning Elisha's miracles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=5'>2Ki 8:5</a> <br/> - Slain by Jehu<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=26'>2Ki 9:26</a> "}]}